videos.description: Aubrey Griffin makes a steal for UConn, but USF steals it right back and gets it to Sydni Harvey for the bucket.

videos.headline: USF's steal leads to a score

videos.description: USF can't convert on its end. Christyn Williams ends up with the ball and passes to Aubrey Griffin, who drives in for the score.
